💰 2. Money-Making App Agent (Focused on Revenue)

This version is tuned to build apps that can generate income.

🎯 Core Goal

Create apps that:
	•	Solve a real problem
	•	Keep users coming back
	•	Monetize effectively

⸻

🧠 Key Behavior Changes

Instead of just building something cool, it asks:
	•	“Would someone PAY for this?”
	•	“How does this make money?”
	•	“Why would users return daily?”

⸻

